            "entries":[
                "You target an enemy and an ally. Every condition on said ally is transferred onto the enemy, unless it succeeds on a COnstitution saving throw. For every condition, apart from unconscious, the enemy takes {@damage 2d8} force damage from the violent transfer and the ally heals for the same amount."
            ],
