            "entries":[
                "You form a 20ft sphere within a space you can see which proceeds to suck the life out of anyone caught within it. Any creature that starts or ends it's turn within the sphere, must make a CON save or suffer {@damage 4d10} necrotic damage.Creatures hit by this ability can not heal or be healed until the start of their next turn.",
                "Half of this damage can then be distributed as you see fit to allies within 60 feet of you."
            ],
            "source":"Ryian",
            "page":1,
