            "entries":[
                "You create an aura that extends 10 feet for the duration around yourself or an ally that hurts the wicked and protects those who fight against such things. When an enemy starts or ends its turn there, it must make a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, the creature takes {@damage 3d8} necrotic or radiant damage (your choice), or half as much on a successful one. Half the damage dealt will then be used as a shield for the righteous as temporary hit points that last for one round. A creature can willing fail this saving throw."
